text: Sum tame evum samaji lidhum che ke tame chodi devamam avaso, jo ke atyara sudhi allaha'e tamara manthi te'one prathamikata nathi api, je'o allahana margamam jehada karanara che, ane jemane allaha ane tena payagambarane ane imanavala'o sivaya ko'ine pana saca mitro nathi banavya, allaha khuba sari rite jane che je kami pana tame kari rahya cho
